---
title: Crystal Cave Skip (CCS)
hidden: false
---
This skip allow the player to skip the the major part of the [crystal cave](http://darksouls.wikidot.com/crystal-cave) leading to [Seath](http://darksouls.wikidot.com/seath-the-scaleless). It is very precise and require a lot of practice for the glitched version.

## External Ressources

### Glitchless Method

The glitchless method saves around 10sec compared to a classic pathing and also allow a better [RTSR](http://darksouls.wikidot.com/red-tearstone-ring) setup.

- Glitchless CCS : [https://youtu.be/mVoS9mI0pYM?t=1773](https://youtu.be/mVoS9mI0pYM?t=1773) by m3dic on YouTube.

### Classic Method (Glitched)

This skip saves around 14sec compared to the glitchless method. Recently some players discovered that the slope qui-out method was easier in mid roll tier.

- CCS using [Slope quitout](/ds1remaster/fall-damages-cancel#slope-quit-out) : [https://youtu.be/X2NwsNKbLY0?t=1490](https://youtu.be/X2NwsNKbLY0?t=1490) by aeiou on YouTube.
- CCS using [memerolls](/ds1remaster/fall-damages-cancel#air-rolls) (very precise, not recommended and slower): [https://youtu.be/Odjz7l62hYQ](https://youtu.be/Odjz7l62hYQ) by San on YouTube.
